main

Class LocationChange

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.LocationChange

  • public class LocationChange
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to store a change in location in both number of steps and degrees to turn. Although it is generally expected to either take steps or to turn in a given move, this isn't restricted, so move and turn could both be set.
